{
  "stem": "4513.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what-- that's what our jobs were and that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw the Rangers when they were going up the side of the cliff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I tell you, that was amazing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, every place you turn, people were-- there was fire coming across the beaches, just like it was sowing seeds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember, I had two fellows, one on each side of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we hid behind a-- a-- a structure, one of the-- those fixtures they put on the beach to keep the ships from coming ashore and the tanks from coming ashore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We hid behind one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know what, you felt like if you hid behind a-- a-- a lump of-- you know, a bit of sand that that will protect you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Any place you could find a place to dive in, you did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went behind this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you know, the most amazing thing-- I'll always remember, the guy on either side of me was killed, and I lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- you know, it's wild.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You say to yourself, how could they miss me and they got those two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But anyway, we finally got up to the-- we got up to the assembly area that had been pre-designated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we-- we pulled them on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, a lot of our guys got killed while that was going on, because obviously they were exposed at the time we were pulling.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we lost a lot of fellas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In fact, by-- in about three or four hours, we had lost all of our officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Every one of them was dead who'd come ashore with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because white officers had a band-- a white band, a vertical band-- behind the ears.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a-- non-commissioned officers-- we had a horizontal band.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
